This ramp closure is necessary to perform investigative coring to determine existing asphalt pavement thickness on the ramp. A detour will be utilized for this ramp closure. A link to the detour map is provided below.&nbsp;This work is part of the&nbsp;continuing construction to&nbsp;replace the I-40 bridges over the Yadkin River and to widen and make improvements along I-40.&nbsp;As always this work is weather dependent and may be subject to change.
